data.description: Stunning home nestled on the hill in Saugatuck! Coveted Spear St dead end and no tourist traffic! This gem has had many updates over the past few years! Newer kitchen and baths, designer lighting & finishes, hardwood floors throughout, fireplace, a/c, newer appliances, on demand hot water, landscaping, decking and patios. Gorgeous private landscaped lot, large porches, decks, fire pit and hot tub. SUPER CUTE SEASONAL 2 BEDROOM COTTAGE ON PROPERTY! This home exudes charm & style and an unbeatable location! Perfect escape, full time home or vacation rental. There is a possibility of a 3rd bedroom on the first floor. Views of Mount Baldhead, Hear the  Star of Saugatuck Whistle, walk to town and Chain Ferry.
